list.item:
For the maintenance of remission of ulcerative colitis in adults, 1.6 g daily, in divided doses (
                                 2.2
                              )

Do not open, crush, break, or chew the capsules. Swallow whole with water (
                                 2.3
                              )

Two DELZICOL 400 mg capsules should not be substituted with one mesalamine delayed-release 800 mg tablet (
                                 2.3
                              )

text.paragraph:
The high dose was not more effective than the low dose and is not an approved dosage [
                           see Dosage and Administration (2.1

                           )].
